					<p>Featuring the two most sought after tee times in all of Ireland--Royal Portrush & Royal County Down. Add to that the authentic Ireland experience of traveling to the far north of Ireland-- off the 'beaten path' where they say, "It's different up here!"</p>

					<p>Fly overnight from your US Gateway to Dublin. On arrival you head north to Rosapenna to get into position for the week ahead. Check into the Rosapenna Hotel for two nights. While at Rosapenna, play a true hidden gem--Portsalon and the Sandy Hills Course at Rosapenna.</p>

